==English==
===Etymology 1===
From Spanish ''[[Tula#Spanish|Tula]]'', from Nahuatl ''[[Tollan#Classical_Nahuatl|Tōllān]]'' "place of [[bulrush]]es", from ''[[tōllin]]'' "bulrush" + ''[[-tlan|-tlān]]''.
====Proper noun====
{{wikipedia|Tula, Hidalgo}}
'''Tula'''

# A town in [[Hidalgo]], [[Mexico]], near the remains of the [[Toltec]] city [[Tollan]].
